comin ' at ya ! is a spanish-american 3d western film , featuring tony anthony , victoria abril and gene quintano and directed by ferdinando baldi .   it was produced as a co-production between american company filmways and the lupo-anthony-quintano company , an independent company .   released in 1981 , the film effectively started the 3d film boom of the early 1980s .   the same filmmakers returned in 1983 with treasure of the four crowns .